<section class="text-block">
    <h3 class="text-block_title">Overview</h3>
    <p class="text-block_role">Role: Discovery, UI Design, HTML/CSS</p>
    <p class="text-block_copy">During our recent refresh of the AWeber brand, I identified an opportunity to update the control panel. After fleshing out the opportunity to the design team, I was given the green-light to lead the redesign and we produced a control panel experience that was on-brand, intuitive, and highly functional.</p>
</section>

