<section class="text-block">
  <h3 class="text-block_title">Challenge</h3>
  <p class="text-block_copy">Our design team didn't have a current style guide so we had to start from scratch. Working with another designer, we spent the first few weeks mapping out our entire control panel experience. We identified the components and shared elements in each area and started defining patterns. My main goal from the redesign was to not only define a basic style guide we could work with but to also create a responsive experience starting mobile-first, which was a major overhaul for our current application.</p>
</section>

<section class="text-block">
  <h3 class="text-block_title">Solution</h3>
  <p class="text-block_copy">In a little under 2 months, we were able to update and define all of the UI elements including fonts, component designs, and colors. In addition to the design and code, we delivered a UI kit which formed the basis for the global AWeber style guide</p>
</section>

